<plot>AMERICAN GAMER follows professional video gamers into the highly competitive, and sometimes murky world of eSports. The high def film combines interviews of the world's best solo and team gamers (Johnathan "Fatal1ty" Wendel) with machinima animation gaming footage to bring the world's most respected eSports tournament to life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?034886</url></doc>
